I guess im pretty good at fucking things up. heh... I dont really know what I did, but I did something and now Danny is in a really shitty mood. I guess I pissed him off er something. dunno

Started school yesterday. Wont last long there. I hate the way it is now. Its a high school. If I wanted to go back to a high school I wouldve went to fucking Corunna this year. I had a goal of going in there and getting my credit and getting out of that place! But now I have to sit there and take classes I DONT need and deal with the stupid people that go there. heh... I was in a VERY shitty mood yesterday. Today i was in a descent mood but Danny wasnt and he got all pissed off when I asked what was wrong and hes like if there was something wrong its not like Im gonna tell you....... thanks. Ever since schools started he acts weird and stuff. I dont like it... If hes gonna be like this all school year then I just wont talk to him.... Not like thats what I want to happen but DAMN!

I was suposed to stay at Dannys tonight but I guess i pissed him off and he told me to go home... well I guess get me a ride and fuck you too....-_-

I want to get my moms camera... I want to take some pictures...like... I dont know weird pictures of things! IDK... But I gotta get the camera outta my dads safe...yeah...Asking my dad for something is like me asking if he could give me $5... not gonna happen.... My dad doesnt seem to like me much anymore... I really dont think many people like me much anymore...

I wounder whats goin on with Kerry....o_O

I feel like shit. My belly hurts.... I wanna blow my head off... I kinda wanna write more then I wanna type in this thing... hmm... IDK But I guess Im done for now I dont know what to bitch about anymore...YAY...-_-

So I think I need to get a job so I can get my own place, and just be like alone I guess. I dont really know what I want. I want a job so I can have some extra money in my pocket... well money period in my pocket. I wanna move out of my parents' home cuz they suck... I guess. I really wanna get my car back on the road... Im thinking about even working at a Bar... something I used to say Id NEVER work at because of my mom.... but I dont really care right now Id rather work at a Bar then no where... and I could prolly get a job at a bar... pretty much anyone can get a job at a fucking bar! I just dont wanna be bitched at anymore for what I do...

My parents dont like the idea of me and Danny hangin out everyday... Why does it matter? Me and Ashley used to hang out everyday 24/7 and they never cared about that. Yeah me and Danny have some problems but we're trying to work on them (or at least I am) it takes time to fix things and change stuff. But they just wanna bitch. His mom bitches about me being over here all the time.... Ok so me and Danny like each other company... fuck off... I guess...

My head hurts....

I havent gotten high today...which isnt normal....(maybe thats why I have a headache...)

Im done with my period but I think Danny's getting ready to start his...

Wednesday I have to go into Pathways to talk to Mrs. Tepper... gotta get my classes... er something...sign some papers... Dannys goin with me cuz hes gotta do the same but he cant sign the papers cuz hes not 18 but his parents will do that later....

The other night I went to my house to stay the night.... Got there around 8 or 9 I think... Went to Penny's got high and came home around 11:00 and my dad bitched and bitched.... he told me doors are locked at 12 it wasnt 12 but he still locked us out including my mom...she was VERY drunk that night... and very pissed at him... anyways he bitched about anything and everything.... talk to my mom.... she bitched about everything and anything. They wounder why I dont like coming home and actually staying there....

I told my dad the other day I wasnt gonna get a job cuz I cant.... He tells me to go to the places I put in apps and get new ones so I can put a different fone number on it... yeah ok.... id like to see him go out and do something of the sort.... Not gonna happen... Not really sure how Im gonna get a job.... I think Ill prolly just go back to the places I know are hiring and get new apps... but who knows if theyre even hiring anymore.... I dont know... Havent been to any of those places since I turned in the apps... this shit sucks ass.... now if my dad didnt go to the bar everynight wed still have our fone....heh... 

ok Im going to bed...just had a few things on my mind that were bothering me.....(and I think Dannys pissed at me) night!

SO! I dont know what to type about today. Theres just too much...heh, I think it would be wounderful if I could like one day go to a different state with out anyone knowing about it and like never come back and no one would know where I was.... But I dont think it'll ever happen. Im more likely to shoot myself then to do that. 

I think Im afraid of guns cuz its like I know if I could get ahold of one I'd be gone. And I know I dont really want to die I just wanna dissapear.  Right now if I had a car Im pretty sure Id be GTFO!

 I still hate myself. I'll say that till I die! heh. 

I dont really feel like talken about much but I feel like I have to or Im gonna blow.... But this journal doesnt help much....I blab in it and what not but I get no where with my shit talking. 

I want some drugs. I think if Geny called me up and asked me if I wanted to hang out I would.... Just cuz I know she can get good drugs and thats all I want right now I wanna be numb. I really dont want to feel. When I was all fucked up everyday I had not a care in the world just wanted to get high. Pills are good for getting the pain away ya know?! Maybe when I get a job Ill save up enough money so when I kill myself or od my parents can pay for my funarl... Or just go somewhere... I'd like to be somewhere else right now not thinking of anything not caring about anything, Id be happy in an ally somewhere with something to numb me.... as long as I couldnt feel anything... 

I dont know how to change myself to something better then this.... I know how to make myself worse, thats easy. But to make my self a different better person............who fucking knows.... Im EMO! As Danny and Tony say... But I guess I am....who cares tho..... 

I woke up this morning with cramps in my stomach and the shits.... isnt that lovely?! I sure thought so... heh...  

Lifes easier on pills.... painless..... I was givin some pills the other day for my head ach... not sure what the where and Danny didnt like the idea of me taken them cuz the person once said they were for back achs and now theyre for head achs... but I didnt care I wanted them... She told me to take one and in like 4 hrs take another one....I took both.... I didnt get SHIT outta it... my headach was still there too.... dumb bitch... 

My mom the other night took a shit load of her pills trying to od.... she woke up the next day.... 

My mom says I can be a storng person.... How can she say that when shes not even strong.... She doesnt know.... She understands what Im going threw but doesnt know what to do about it cuz she cant even make her self strong... 

When I get sent to the hospital for an od... I get bitched at cuz my dad has another hospital bill.... 

Danny said something the other day.... "Only if we had friends" only if we did... Things are suposed to change between us.... is it? has it?

 I dont know why all this shit just like hit me... I was fine playing my game and then all of the sudden I went DOWN.... and I smoked a bowl hopen to go back up and now I just wanna cry and cry.... If I was at my house I prolly would be but cuz Im sitting right next to Danny I can.... 

I wanna be held. I wanna be a dog or some kind of animal... A wild animal so I dont have someone there saying NO.... I just go... a Turtle! a very big one so no one messes with me!

Only if I had some money right now....and my car... Id be at pennys tryin to mooch her pills....

I need to build a wall...

The other night Martin grabed me and just started huggin me for no reason just outta no where... It felt good to have someone hold me. I dont like Martin his a good friend but it just felt good to have someone somewhat close to me hug me just because....

I gotta get a job so I can get my car back on the damn road. But it wont happen for awhile.... I really dont think Ill be getting a job anytime soon.... I really dont think Ill be going any where with my life anytime soon... Im stuck... 

I wont have a computer here soon... Dannys sisters movin in here and shes gonna need dannys computer room and his bed room wont fit 2 puters and his bed and what not so I gotta take mine home....

I know Kathy doesnt want me and Danny to be friends anymore.... I dont think she wants me here half the time... oh well what am I suposed to do?! Just another person down the drain.... heh I dont even know who my best friend is anymore..... 

Speeking of whom... Ashley had her baby... very very cute! She got married too.... I dont know what Im suposed to do.... everythings changeing with me and her soo damn fast I dont get it.... I cant go to her house when her hubbies there cuz he dont like me and when I go over there when hes not there I feel like she dont want me there.... I hope one day she realizes whats goin on... I dont have a best friend anymore... I have Danny and I cant say hes my best friend... Sometimes I cant even say hes my friend.... Sometimes I cant even say I know him....

Cant I be like 7 again? I dont know what its like to be a 7 year old KID.... I WISH! Thats all I can do... what ever I wish for or want i dont get.... I usually say you want it bad enough you can get it..... Ive been wanting the samething for who knows how long and still havent gotten it... pointless.... Just like my purpose here....pointless, Im just taken up air and room....

I think Im gonna take a shower sometime tonight or a bath....

I can feel the razor on my air.... omg how i want it so bad.... but I guess I wont do it..... I have enough scars for now.... I could use another burn but that wont happen either... I wont be allowed at Dannys house again.... So he says.... But to see blood comin out of my arm would make me feel so much better right now.... or some pills... I was just telling Danny I was worried about him cuz hes been wanted to get pills a lot lately and just the way he talks about it.... But look at me I want pills to make the pain go away he wants them to have a little fun not because hes depressed.....heh

Theres nothing here for me....

Im pathetic...

I WANT MY CAR!!! god damn my cuz....

I think once I get home Im gonna get some shorts and a cool shirt on and just chill. I didnt know it was so hot out side when I woke up and got dressed... Its nice and cool in my house but once I stepped out side I was like WHOA! Time to take the pants off! =p

Theres my rambling on about nothingness for today! GOOD DAY!!....................I SAID GOOD DAY!

Im tired and Id somewhat like to just fall asleep and not wake up. 

I hate the fact that I have to stress about everything. My moms been laid off pretty much. Because of her ONE resriction. My dads in jail untill the morning of my birthday. 

Id like to go back to my counsler and what not but I dont want to be stuck on meds Id just like to be able to talk I guess and maybe get a little help. But meds dont seem to work with me. My problem isnt a chemical inbalance I never had a fucking father and pills arent gonna help change that.

Oh yeah I dont know if I've said anything before but me and Danny are back together and so far so good. A little more then a month now. We're doing ok but I wish he'd agknolage it a little more but he seems SOO much more happy now...Ive seen him smile a lot more now then I have in a long ass time... but I dont know. He seems happy with me and what not... I know I feel a lot happier then what I used to feel... me and danny being happy is prolly the only thing thats going good for me in my life and its GREAT but ya know Id like to not have to stress about my fucking family. I dont know how Im suposed to EVER have my own life if I keep stressing about my parents and shit. I wish I could fix it... arg 

I'll be getting my licens here pretty soon hopfully. 

Its sad that Dan and Kathy have to move outta this house. I like this house and I know they do and this house used to be MY home too... =( They have to get rid of cloud and ozzy...=( I cryed when moomoo told me that. I love those cats!

Awhile ago moomoo bought me a sound card for my computer so now I have SOUND! YAY! lotsa music on my puter. I might have to take it back to my house cuz Danny might not have enough room for it in his room but I guess we're gonna see. I hope he does! I like playing W.o.W. its fun! =D

I feel bad but yesterday I went over to her house to see what she got but NO I couldnt come in and check it out cuz her stupid b/f was on his way home from work and he dont like me cuz I told Ashley that he tired to get in my pants. Well the mother fucker might be going to jail cuz he was fucking around with Alisha and her mom called the po po's on him.... Im losing my best friend because of a fucking guy and its bull shit. Danny told me I should talk to her but I dont think its gonna work cuz shes in love with him and what not. Im just her neighbor now. 

I have one friend left and thats Danny and the mother fuckers slowly but shurly getting my trust back.

Im getting ready to start here soon and damn it I need to so It will be done by the time my birthday comes around! 

Well I guess Im done for now with this blabbing of mine
I hate myself and I want to die

WOW. So I havent typed in this in a long ass time... heh... I write alot more now. Nothing new has been goin on. My dad has to move out. Him and my brother got into it again and my brother did the most damage but my dad started it. Me and Danny were'nt friends fer awhile there and then kinda started being friends again.... Ive been at his house for like 3 weeks to a month. Tryin to get my schooling done and this is the only place I know I'll have a ride. I think I got a small case of food poisioning yesterday and still today. Its not fun lemme tell ya! If Danny decides he doesnt want to try one last time (3 times a charm?) then I dont think Im gonna be here much longer... I dont want to get close to him just for him to push me away in the long run ya know. I gotta talk to him about it but I cant get the balls to do so.  Idk... oh well Im done for now. BYE
